      "span_text": "In this issue of Circulation: Cardiovascular Imaging, Shreibati et al  present the findings of an excellent and muchneeded analysis that leverages a propensity score method to evaluate the clinical impact of CAC imaging relative to the alternatives of hs-CRP testing and lipid screening."
